 * Route for creating a new user
 * # API
 * - Endpoint: `/api/users`
 * - Verb: POST
 * - Success Code: 201
 *
 * @typedef {function} Route-CreateUser
 * @param {Object} req - Express request object

 *                          error message
 * @param {number} res.status - Indicates success or not
